### Get all item groups
GET http://localhost:5000/api/itemgroups
Content-Type: application/json

### Get a specific item group by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/itemgroups/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Add a new item group
POST http://localhost:5000/api/itemgroups
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Software",
